<ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Americans</ENAMEX> place native or native speakers in charge of subsidiaries overseas .
<ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">European</ENAMEX> multinationals do likewise ; even in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">America</ENAMEX> , their affiliates are usually run by <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">American</ENAMEX> managers .
